Platform-Web Repo-Size Tech-Stack


ðŸ“‘ Description
Type Master is an online game to test your typing skills.

ðŸŽ® Playing Instructions
Random word is generated and user needs to type it within the given time frame (10 seconds initially).
Next word is generated as soon as user types the correct word and additional 3 seconds are added to the remaining time frame.
On reaching score of 15 and 25 instaed of adding 3 seconds 1 second is reduced from the timer to make it more difficult.
This goes on till the timer runs out or user reaches a maximum score of 30.
Note: Score of 15 and 25 on the scoreboard acts as a checkpoint to increase the difficulty. Maximum Score is 30.
